# AAP Config-as-Code Bundle

This directory was generated from the active AAP migration project and is intended for disaster recovery and environment recreation.

## Contents

- group_vars/all.yml: installer and endpoint variables captured from source project.
- inventories/production.ini: inventory scaffold generated from current inventory groups.
- playbooks/recreate_aap_environment.yml: install and validate playbook.
- exports/*.json: exported AAP controller objects (organizations, inventories, projects, job templates) when API token is available.

## Run

```bash
ansible-playbook -i inventories/production.ini playbooks/recreate_aap_environment.yml
```

For imported controller data, use your preferred import workflow (for example infra.controller_configuration.dispatch).
